## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a1765-117">때 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A> 반환 범위 있는지 확인 하 여 검사를 수행 해야는 `pointer` 매개 변수는 `null`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a1765-117">When <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A> returns, you should perform bounds checking by verifying that the `pointer` parameter is `null`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a1765-118">없으면 `null`를 호출 해야 합니다는 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.ReleasePointer%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> (CER) 제약이 있는 실행 영역에는 메서드.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a1765-118">If it is not `null`, you must call the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.ReleasePointer%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method in a constrained execution region (CER).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a1765-119"><xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A> 호출 된 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeHandle.DangerousAddRef%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 메서드 포인터를 노출 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a1765-119"><xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A> calls the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeHandle.DangerousAddRef%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method and exposes the pointer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a1765-120">와 달리는 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.Read%2A> 메서드, 포인터의 현재 위치를 변경 하지 않습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a1765-120">Unlike the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.Read%2A> method, it does not change the current position of the pointer.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a1765-121">다음 exampledemonstrates 사용 하는 방법의 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A> 메서드:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a1765-121">The following exampledemonstrates how to use the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A> method:</span></span>  
  
```  
byte* pointer = null;  
RuntimeHelpers.PrepareConstrainedRegions();  
try {  
    MySafeBuffer.AcquirePointer(ref pointer);  
    // Use pointer here, with your own bounds checking.  
    }  
finally {  
    if (pointer != null)  
        MySafeBuffer.ReleasePointer();  
    }  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a1765-122">캐스팅 하는 경우 `pointer` (되는 바이트에 대 한 포인터)를 다른 유형 (T \*) 포인터로 포인터 맞춤 문제가 있을 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a1765-122">If you cast `pointer` (which is a pointer to a byte) as a pointer to a different type (T\*), you may have pointer alignment issues.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a1765-123">이 포인터를 확인 하 여 모든 범위에 대 한 책임을 수행 해야 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a1765-123">You must take responsibility for all bounds checking with this pointer.</span></span>

